老打我尖上巴士<br />\n俾我大大聲叫佢排隊<br />\n佢死死氣地排返隊<br />\n之後我塞住耳仔由得佢係咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcf82dc5eaa83cf86feee53382fcdbec2b308a9","tid":408193,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"請先讓有需要人士登車"},{"pid":"dc83bb01eab160f3131213ee750ef121bcfe61f1","tid":408193,"uid":118093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"我通常會好有禮貌咁叫佢地欄過去排隊<br />\n多數d 廢老都肯聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1479e1dccff50b595914917c15f636d7c0faf1","tid":408193,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"啲廢老最鍾意攝位上車  攝位落車"},{"pid":"9d7e0eb55ffe5d36a95a2dad23373f43b69bbf67","tid":408193,"uid":35460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77e70ecd9b68f84918ef680f46c843b5ea75bc92","tid":408193,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最可恨係成班人冇個企出黎屌佢老母而只係識網上開post</blockquote><br />\n你又無知我企出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無野既<br />\n我假如比人打尖上唔上到到都會走上車<br />\n企定定係條仆街隔離<br />\n屌到佢落返為止</blockquote><br />\n岩岩呢劑我上到車，照話佢，點知比半車老野插返轉頭唔敬老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f8030384b191bf063ff400841f356c51bbf71e","tid":408193,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"企第一二個都仲有辦法迫班仆街排返隊尾<br />\n但企後咗就無符了"},{"pid":"c6699bf0ac42ff1dcb5ea57f582af662c6baf2f0","tid":408193,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"上次排隊等巴士，得3條友排，有個阿伯就坐係巴士站後面啲花槽邊。架車一來個死老野一支箭衝去想上車，我就一鳩閘住佢話叫佢排隊，點知個死老野竟然話我仲來得早過你啦。我無理佢就上左車啦,後面果兩個人就俾個死仆街打左尖。<br />\n啲死老鬼真係唔死都無撚用，得三個人排隊都要打尖，仲要聲大大咁，正仆街！"},{"pid":"d954955b8561b2b202846073b977fe0f296c0449","tid":408193,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請先讓有需要人士登車</blockquote><br />\n開返條關愛隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259a7bffb6428ba0085b03ed33931c7231608bff","tid":408193,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:21:01.000Z","msg":"趕住先行一步，係咁架啦"},{"pid":"5bd31b98858340bd4c0d652a932aa38376778d9d","tid":408193,"uid":10280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"明明一路排緊隊，但一到上車嗰下就會湧去你前面，好似係我阻住佢上車咁，唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31637f49e9a2a3cdddd1df19456c0b249628761d","tid":408193,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最可恨係成班人冇個企出黎屌佢老母而只係識網上開post</blockquote><br />\n你又知人地無屌？"},{"pid":"356b704c055a5ff2a5f11de81c010c7588ea7db6","tid":408193,"uid":18949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明一路排緊隊，但一到上車嗰下就會湧去你前面，好似係我阻住佢上車咁，唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隧道口都係。仆街條隊廿幾三十人，一野屌到但阿伯車都無上"},{"pid":"68ea44686dc3df0051b543022ecdcd50fa7da21d","tid":408193,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:29:49.000Z","msg":"佢地怕蝕底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但廢老又最鐘意老點後生：唔好怕蝕底"},{"pid":"adac55e5123994edfd2e9063d6ec3d0312aa5ce9","tid":408193,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最可恨係成班人冇個企出黎屌佢老母而只係識網上開post</blockquote><br />\n你又無知我企出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無野既<br />\n我假如比人打尖上唔上到到都會走上車<br />\n企定定係條仆街隔離<br />\n屌到佢落返為止</blockquote><br />\n岩岩呢劑我上到車，照話佢，點知比半車老野插返轉頭唔敬老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n敬老養你訓棺材囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0df39fdda8a73aa390cba8b52cda7a65247e7a2","tid":408193,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"而定最興扮傻行上前問人呢架車係咪去XXX/扮睇資料<br />\n<br />\n仲有招無等小巴 企埋去前面但唔上住 我下一部黎排最前"},{"pid":"9dede4e89e3e8b66a77629c526baf79e35b447ee","tid":408193,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而定最興扮傻行上前問人呢架車係咪去XXX/扮睇資料<br />\n<br />\n仲有招無等小巴 企埋去前面但唔上住 等下一部黎排最前</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5384fcd3b5637d33f648f17ae35db592d59d645b","tid":408193,"uid":137990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"試過又係咁俾班廢老打尖<br />\n個巴士司機唔肯開門用手指住佢地做口形示意要佢地排隊<br />\n班廢老見到都乖乖地排隊<br />\n除左有一個仆街阿婆係扮排隊 等司機開門就推開哂佢身邊既廢老衝左上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e38eb39e73679498ccc682cdc2e707bef2fff7","tid":408193,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明一路排緊隊，但一到上車嗰下就會湧去你前面，好似係我阻住佢上車咁，唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日係咁"}]}